strings: <voice_0x01001CD2><se_high>media princess: Welcome to dreamland. <hero> Thank you for the opportunity to speak!
<voice_0x01001CD3><se_high>media princess: We are so happy to have Jessica back with us.
<voice_0x01001CD4><se_high>media princess: My father and I are still cursed.
<voice_0x01001CD5><se_high>media princess: Sometimes we ask ourselves<:> How are we going to spend the rest of our lives?
<voice_0x01001CD6><se_high>media princess: sorry My heart aches every time I think of those nails.
<voice_0x01001CD7><se_high>media princess: But did you get what happened? <hero> Don't let the curse get past you.
<voice_0x01001CD8><se_high>media princess: It is not, however, a miracle. I always knew that you had something special <hero>.
<voice_0x01001CD9><se_high>media princess: Please take me to the spring some day. I would like to talk...
